<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 12:25:01 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>台湾总统将访问中国紧张局势中心的前线岛屿</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-president-visit-frontline-islands-centre-china-tensions-2024-08-22/</link><description>台湾总统赖清德将于周五对敏感的金门群岛进行自五月上任以来的首次访问。金门群岛毗邻中国海岸，也是台北和北京之间紧张局势加剧的地方。</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 10:43:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-president-visit-frontline-islands-centre-china-tensions-2024-08-22/</guid></item><item><title>中国平安上半年利润增长6.8%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-ping-an-insurance-posts-68-rise-first-half-profit-2024-08-22/</link><description>中国平安公布上半年净利润增长 6.8%，主要受新保单增长以及在市场波动中采取长期投资举措的推动。</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 10:11:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-ping-an-insurance-posts-68-rise-first-half-profit-2024-08-22/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：美元之王的王冠正在滑落</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-2024-08-22/</link><description>达拉·拉纳辛格 (Dhara Ranasinghe) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望。</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 10:05:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-2024-08-22/</guid></item><item><title>由于中国经济放缓影响广告支出，百度第二季度营收持平</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinas-baidu-beats-quarterly-revenue-estimates-2024-08-22/</link><description>搜索引擎巨头百度周四公布的季度收入持平，原因是经济低迷打压了广告商支出。</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 09:04:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinas-baidu-beats-quarterly-revenue-estimates-2024-08-22/</guid></item><item><title>印度7月份超越中国成为俄罗斯最大石油买家</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/india-surpasses-china-become-russias-top-oil-buyer-july-2024-08-22/</link><description>进口数据比较显示，7月份印度取代中国成为全球最大的俄罗斯石油进口国，因为中国炼油厂因生产燃料的利润率较低而减少了购买量。</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 08:34:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/india-surpasses-china-become-russias-top-oil-buyer-july-2024-08-22/</guid></item><item><title>关于中国扩大对欧盟进口产品的调查你需要了解什么</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/what-you-need-know-about-chinas-widening-probe-eu-imports-2024-08-22/</link><description>在欧盟发布针对中国制造的电动汽车（EV）的修订关税计划的第二天，中国对欧盟奶酪、牛奶和奶油进口展开反补贴调查，增加了对欧盟白兰地和猪肉的调查。</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 07:37:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/what-you-need-know-about-chinas-widening-probe-eu-imports-2024-08-22/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，普华永道中国因恒大审计面临6个月业务禁令和巨额罚款</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/pwc-china-faces-6-mth-business-ban-large-fine-over-evergrande-audit-sources-say-2024-08-22/</link><description>五名消息人士称，中国监管机构可能会下令普华永道在中国大陆的大部分审计部门暂停业务六个月，作为对陷入困境的房地产开发商恒大集团的惩罚的一部分。</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 07:33:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/pwc-china-faces-6-mth-business-ban-large-fine-over-evergrande-audit-sources-say-2024-08-22/</guid></item><item><title>外交部：中方反对任何国家允许达赖喇嘛访华</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-says-opposes-any-country-allowing-dalai-lama-make-visits-2024-08-22/</link><description>中国外交部发言人周四表示，中方坚决反对任何国家以任何借口允许达赖喇嘛出访。</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 07:26:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-says-opposes-any-country-allowing-dalai-lama-make-visits-2024-08-22/</guid></item><item><title>中国证实日本公民因涉嫌间谍活动被起诉</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-confirms-japanese-citizen-indicted-suspicion-espionage-2024-08-22/</link><description>中国外交部周四表示，中国检方以涉嫌间谍罪对一名日本公民提起公诉，并补充称涉案人员的权利将得到保护。</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 07:25:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-confirms-japanese-citizen-indicted-suspicion-espionage-2024-08-22/</guid></item><item><title>中国称其在台湾海峡监视并警告美国驱逐舰</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uss-ralph-johnson-made-routine-taiwan-strait-transit-says-us-navy-2024-08-22/</link><description>中国军方表示，周四一艘美国驱逐舰驶过台湾海峡时，它对其进行了监视和警告，这是最近一次此类穿越敏感水道的行为，令北京感到不安。</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 05:46:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/uss-ralph-johnson-made-routine-taiwan-strait-transit-says-us-navy-2024-08-22/</guid></item><item><title>随着中国威胁加剧，台湾国防支出将超过GDP增长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-defence-spend-outpace-gdp-growth-china-threat-rises-2024-08-22/</link><description>台湾内阁周四表示，台湾明年的国防开支将增长 7.7%，超过预期的经济增长，因为台湾将增加更多战斗机和导弹，以加强对北京日益严重的威胁的威慑。</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 04:35:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-defence-spend-outpace-gdp-growth-china-threat-rises-2024-08-22/</guid></item><item><title>美国敦促日本任命救灾中心工作组成员</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/japan/us-urges-japan-name-disaster-relief-hub-task-force-members-2024-08-22/</link><description>美国周三呼吁日本任命联合特遣部队的代表，该特遣部队将确定他们同意在日本建立的人道主义援助和救灾中心的地点和资源。</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 03:48:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/japan/us-urges-japan-name-disaster-relief-hub-task-force-members-2024-08-22/</guid></item><item><title>韦世豪落选中国队世界杯预选赛大名单</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/wei-shihao-left-out-china-squad-world-cup-qualifiers-2024-08-22/</link><description>左翼球员韦世豪因在中超联赛中犯规而被禁赛四场，因此被排除在中国下个月对阵日本和沙特阿拉伯的世界杯预选赛大名单之外。</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 03:38:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/wei-shihao-left-out-china-squad-world-cup-qualifiers-2024-08-22/</guid></item><item><title>对中国对欧盟乳制品反补贴调查的反应</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/reactions-chinas-anti-subsidy-probe-eu-dairy-imports-2024-08-22/</link><description>在欧盟修改中国制造的电动汽车关税计划的第二天，中国对从欧盟进口的乳制品发起反补贴调查。</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 03:31:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/reactions-chinas-anti-subsidy-probe-eu-dairy-imports-2024-08-22/</guid></item><item><title>中国恒大子公司交易提高了离岸债权人的前景</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/china-evergrande-subsidiary-dealings-raises-prospects-offshore-creditors-2024-08-22/</link><description>专家表示，如果中国恒大的境外债权人能够证明该房地产开发商是来自境内子公司的应付款，他们因此有权获得这笔资金，那么他们可能会增加收回资金的机会。</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 02:56:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/china-evergrande-subsidiary-dealings-raises-prospects-offshore-creditors-2024-08-22/</guid></item></channel></rss>